{"tid":1763238,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從事 [物業管理] 都有得投功能界別","createTime":"2019-11-30T07:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T09:40:02.000Z","uid":265211,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ff51134b220556620aadfcbb19359287bb086248","tid":1763238,"uid":265211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:33:08.000Z","msg":"簡單講，就係入<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港測量師學會 (HKIS)</span>的物業設施管理組 (PFMD)，入到會做正式會員 (MHKIS)就有<span style=\"color: blue;\">建測規園界</span>張票。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">入會方法一：考入去</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你有相關學歷，就可以開Log Book，寫兩年Log Book之後就考paper (Practical Task)。Pass咗就寫篇唔多於4千字的Final Assessment。搞掂哂交埋會費就成功，歷時要三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAPC詳細說明書：<a href=\"https://www.hkis.org.hk/hkis/papers/pfm-apcpt2017.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkis.org.hk%2Fhkis%2Fpapers%2Fpfm-apcpt2017.pdf&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf70p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=0a1ce534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkis.org.hk/hkis/papers/pfm-apcpt2017.pdf</a><br />\nPractical Task Past Paper：<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GUitVFmEKI4Ib_aWFG6hYRiDHV1GpxHM/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1GUitVFmEKI4Ib_aWFG6hYRiDHV1GpxHM%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf70p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=2f3101c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GUitVFmEKI4Ib_aWFG6hYRiDHV1GpxHM/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">入會方法二：經HKIH入RICS，再經RICS入HKIS</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你本身已經係MHKIH而又qualified咗五年，就可以申請RICS，經過ethics assessment，交會費就入到會。<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&quot;Members of the HKIH (F.H.K.I.H. and M.H.K.I.H.) with five years post-qualification, and successful completion of the RICS ethics assessment prior to admission&quot;</span></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rics.org/en-hk/news-insight/latest-news/press-releases/rics-and-hkih-announce-mutual-recognition-of-professional-membership/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rics.org%2Fen-hk%2Fnews-insight%2Flatest-news%2Fpress-releases%2Frics-and-hkih-announce-mutual-recognition-of-professional-membership%2F&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf70p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=9a2539de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rics.org/en-hk/news-insight/latest-news/press-releases/rics-and-hkih-announce-mutual-recognition-of-professional-membership/</a><br />\n<br />\n入咗RICS一年之後，就申請入HKIS，再加interview就得。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>．one year post-qualification as a Chartered Facilities Management Surveyor and professional practice in Hong Kong relevant to the Property &amp; Facility Management Division of HKIS.<br />\n．a professional interview conducted at the discretion of HKIS to verify the applicant's competence and suitability for admission to the Division.</em></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rics.org/en-hk/news-insight/latest-news/press-releases/rics-and-hkis-mutual-recognition-in-facilities-management/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rics.org%2Fen-hk%2Fnews-insight%2Flatest-news%2Fpress-releases%2Frics-and-hkis-mutual-recognition-in-facilities-management%2F&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf70p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=cf3907d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rics.org/en-hk/news-insight/latest-news/press-releases/rics-and-hkis-mutual-recognition-in-facilities-management/</a><br />\n<br />\n感覺好燒錢，不過對比建築師學會、香港工業總會(工業界第一功能界別)，HKIS會費唔算好貴。求求你哋認真考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />建測規園多你一票真係好多，係目前最有可能翻盤的一個界別!"},{"pid":"3b9b497f51f8cb1d45b49f3f2e673f291f2cf2d0","tid":1763238,"uid":36826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,